6.00	Hanasakeru_Seish%C5%8Dnen	Hanasakeru Seishōnen	Hanasakeru Seishōnen ) is a manga series written and illustrated by Natsumi Itsuki. Set in the modern era, the story follows the path to romance of fourteen-year-old Kajika Burnsworth, daughter of powerful industrialist Harry Burnsworth, owner of the Burnsworth international conglomerate giant. Kajika agrees to participate in a "marriage game" with her father, in which she must select her future husband out of three men that her father has supposedly preselected for her.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/9/94/Hanasakeru_Seish%C5%8Dnen_vol01.jpg/230px-Hanasakeru_Seish%C5%8Dnen_vol01.jpg
